comments: Dragic (MIA) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
During the rebound, Dragic (MIA) swings his off-arm back and makes contact to Bertans' (WAS) head/neck area.
Hachimura (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Butler's (MIA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Adebayo (MIA) makes contact with Beal's (WAS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hachimura (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Butler (MIA) during the drive.
Len (WAS) contests the shot by Adebayo (MIA) and marginal contact occurs to his arm after the release that does not affect his shot in the lane.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests Len's (WAS) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is deemed incidental.
Hachimura (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt by Butler (MIA).
After Hachimura (WAS) secures the rebound, Olynyk (MIA) makes clean ball contact to tie the ball up and a jump ball is correctly whistled.
During the jump ball, Dragic (MIA) and Smith (WAS) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Butler (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Bertans' (WAS) path and absorbs the contact.
Bertans (WAS) legally contests Dragic's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
During the rebound, Len (WAS) and Adebayo (MIA) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Smith (WAS) releases from contact with Dragic (MIA) and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Smith (WAS) attempts the jump shot and any contact by Dragic (MIA) during his upward shooting motion is marginal.
Len (WAS) moves towards Dragic (MIA) but Dragic initiates the marginal contact during his driving shot attempt when he jumps into Len.
Olynyk (MIA) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
Butler (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Brown Jr.'s (WAS) path and absorbs the contact.
After Beal (WAS) secures the rebound, the game clock expires as Adebayo (MIA) tries to cleanly tie the ball up.
